.worktrees/

# Sickbay runtime cache — ignore at any depth so apps/* and packages/*
# don't accidentally commit their self-scan output (last-report.json
# leaks absolute paths, dep-tree.json and history.json are derived state).
# The previous anchored `.sickbay/*.json` patterns only matched the root,
# which is how apps/cli/.sickbay/{dep-tree,last-report}.json slipped in.
**/.sickbay/history.json
**/.sickbay/last-report.json
**/.sickbay/dep-tree.json
**/.sickbay/cache/

# Fixtures' .sickbay/ is intentionally tracked so snapshot regression
# tests stay deterministic. Negate the ignore for that path only.
!fixtures/**/.sickbay/history.json
!fixtures/**/.sickbay/last-report.json
!fixtures/**/.sickbay/dep-tree.json
